eNCA senior reporter, Slindelo Masikane is in Braamfontein #Dstv403 JOHANNESBURG - Students at Wits University are vowing to intensify their protests. They're angry at financial exclusions and ongoing housing issues at the institution. University management says it will act firmly against those who disrupt teaching and learning. The SRC announced a campus shutdown until their grievances are addressed. #eNCA's Silindelo Masikane reports. #DStv403